metadata.name: Deca Palette Salad #1
metadata.description: Deca Palette Salad 3d NFT is a one-of-a-kind project that celebrates the gift of CC0 from Deca.art. This 3d NFT was created specifically for use on platforms like Spatial.io and Oncyber.io, and will be available for download on Darkblock.io. The NFT is created from 54 colors using 9 different, well-known artist's palettes, and there are only 100 models. Each 3d model features a unique palette fingerprint or pixel arrangement on the Deca logo in the centre. Unique Holder only extras that can be unlocked on www.darkblock.io with a monthly artwork made available. Airdrop of a RCS 3D model to original minters of DPS. Please read more in this Medium article what you can expect: https://medium.com/@MorpheusSomnia/dps-rcs-collab-34f162f905de?source=friends_link&sk=586e289e4d2ee32a985811a85e1b1103
